{
  "comment_text": {
    "sn4.15:2.2": "Elsewhere there are mind-made deities who are said to “wander in midair” (<i lang='pi' translate='no'>antalikkhacara</i>, <a href='https://suttacentral.net/dn1/en/sujato#2.2.3'>DN 1:2.2.3</a>). The idea goes back to the Vedas (eg. Rig Veda 6.58.3, <i lang='pi' translate='no'>antarikṣe caranti</i>). "
  },
